>> source: https://thesaltymarshmallow.com/best-homemade-alfredo-sauce/
>> serves: 2 cups
>> total time: 10 minutes

Add the @butter{1/2%cup} and @heavy whipping cream{1.5%cups} to a #large skillet{}.

Simmer over low heat for ~{2%minutes}.

Whisk in the @garlic{2%tsp}, @Italian seasoning{1/2%tsp}, @salt{1/2%tsp}, and @pepper{1/4%tsp} for ~{1%minute}.

Whisk in the @Parmesan{2%cups} cheese until melted.

Serve immediately.
